snippet: A suicide bomber exploded his vehicle at an arms bazaar in northwestern Pakistan on Saturday, killing 16 people and wounding 15, a senior government official said.
abstract: Suicide bomber explodes his vehicle at arms bazaar in northwestern Pakistan, killing 16 people and wounding 15; victims are mostly local tribesmen.
lead_paragraph: A suicide bomber exploded his vehicle at an arms bazaar in northwestern Pakistan on Saturday, killing 16 people and wounding 15, a senior government official said.
